OL,3,C'Top secret' surprise for D-Day
OL,4,Cveteran celebrating 100th birthday
OL,6,FHis centenary was celebrated at
OL,7,FNynehead Court Care Home, near
OL,8,FWellington.
OL,10,FThe Vice-Lieutenant of Somerset, Ted
OL,11,FAllen, was there to thank Lt Willis on
OL,12,Fbehalf of the King for his war service.
OL,14,F"It's an honour for me to be here
OL,15,Ftoday to celebrate the milestone
OL,16,Fbirthday of a remarkable man," Mr
OL,17,FAllen said.
