OL,3,C'Top secret' surprise for D-Day
OL,4,Cveteran celebrating 100th birthday
OL,6,F"The country owes all our veterans an
OL,7,Fenormous debt of gratitude and it was
OL,8,Fa joy for me to be able to express
OL,9,Fthat gratitude on behalf of His
OL,10,FMajesty."
OL,12,FThe Lieutenancy organised for the
OL,13,Fveteran to be presented with a D-Day
OL,14,Fchart of the Utah beach landings,
OL,15,Fprepared by the UK Hydrographic Office
OL,16,Fand held in its archives in Taunton.
