OL,3,C'Top secret' surprise for D-Day
OL,4,Cveteran celebrating 100th birthday
OL,6,FTwo other former senior military
OL,7,Fofficers ` Rear Admiral Ian Moncrieff
OL,8,Fand Brigadier Richard Toomey, both
OL,9,FDeputy Lieutenants in Somerset ` were
OL,10,Falso present at the birthday
OL,11,Fcelebrations.
OL,13,FAfter leaving the Royal Navy, Lt
OL,14,FWillis became a professional artist
OL,15,Fand his work ` particularly in
OL,16,Fmaritime art ` achieved high acclaim.
OL,18,FMuch of his work was influenced by his
OL,19,Fwartime experiences and he was the
OL,20,Fyoungest ever exhibitor at the Royal
OL,21,FAcademy of Arts in 1942.
